足自己本身又難戒的話，就應該考慮策略性放過。唔係搞罷食黎而又失敗盞比對家笑、內部又產生挫敗感。<br />\n<br />\n至於「放過」既合理性，在於實際左我地係冇可能一下子可以放棄所有藍店。因為我地要面對一個現實就係，有d野的確係難以一時三刻可以停用。所以由容易既目標落手，例如TVB。應該根據返「對黃色經濟圈既幫助」同「對藍營/中資既損害」作為選擇罷買目標既標準。"},{"pid":"5d11f3bda276e53ac34a46cc9cbaf674fd6f0d34","tid":1810430,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:02:36.000Z","msg":"相比起罷食，其實有d更有力既野可以做。例如（一）眾籌成立主權基金購買鋪位、業務，協助完整黃色產業鏈。（二）建立黃色電子貨幣平台，將整個消費生活電子化，並穩定係黃色經濟圈內。"},{"pid":"defdfc49eab2ecc044dece08b83671cf1ae6fb7a","tid":1810430,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0152f486469f227c61b1c39dbd9d4678c79f6f6e","tid":1810430,"uid":201581,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:23:36.000Z","msg":"Cls，一有優惠啲人就好似成世未食過m記咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罷食啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:52:03.000Z","msg":"200萬人以外 仲有500萬港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ffb171d1a0da4b4deb6a2bd861093c38a81480","tid":1810430,"uid":73515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T19:44:07.000Z","msg":"煮飯煮麥樂雞年年都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cb7c09f79a638f4bf89e15aaf4a47728ad79fc","tid":1810430,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T21:30:13.000Z","msg":"終於有人做 <br />\nThank you"},{"pid":"986ead2d0f44ea6ffe9db2670584beaad7a572f0","tid":1810430,"uid":97840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T23:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ExUayj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ExUayj.png&h=325a750e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccb181144bcc432aaab74aa5c44a437def6ad126","tid":1810430,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T23:41:56.000Z